---
// Resource hints emitted high in <head> on every page. The webfonts (Playfair
// Display, Outfit, JetBrains Mono) load via an @import in the site CSS, which
// is render-blocking AND can't even open the gstatic.com socket until that CSS
// has parsed. A preconnect opens the TLS handshake to both Google Fonts hosts
// up front, shaving the font round-trip off first paint.
//
//   • fonts.googleapis.com serves the stylesheet (a same-origin-ish CSS fetch)
//     → a plain preconnect.
//   • fonts.gstatic.com serves the actual .woff2 files over CORS → preconnect
//     WITH crossorigin, or the warmed socket can't be reused for the font fetch.
//
// Starlight docs pages get the same two hints via the `head` config in
// astro.config.mjs; this component covers the standalone Astro routes.
---

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
